{
  "stem": "71.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my name is Sally Marco.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My name-- maiden name is Landowicz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was born in Lodz, Poland November 1923, if you want to know exact my date.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "November 11.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was in a large industrial town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Population was approximately 600,000 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were quite over 200,000 Jews residing at-- before the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after ghetto was formed, a lot of people were sent out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then other people were sent in from different countries like Germany, and Austria, and our adjoining little towns, when they liquidated.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it kept on being like 200 population almost all the time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Ajzyk Jacov Landovitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother's name was Esther Landovitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were eight sisters and a brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my oldest sister was [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Raica, ?] then was Devora, and Mindel, and Jochewed, and myself, and my brother-- my brother Joseph was older than I was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then was my sister Regina, and Ruth, and Lea who did not live through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the only ones who survived are Jochewed, myself, Regina, and Ruth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The rest perished during the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My brother died in Feldafing 10 days after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we found his grave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we put a matzevah on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then my sister that was older than I, Perl, she died shortly before the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And a newspaper was sent to me, and her name-- somebody found the grave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and her name was on the-- on the grave.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So apparently it was-- must have been very shortly before the end of war that they took the time to put the name on the grave.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were a middle age-- middle-- middle class family.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was a businessman, and he dealt in a business with the government.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a government business.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
